    "What makes ALM different from ChatGPT?<|assistant|ALM is built from scratch with its own architecture - it doesn't use any existing model as a base. Key differences: MoE architecture for task-adaptive processing, online learning that updates weights from conversations, focused training on coding and creative writing instead of bloated general knowledge, and it can run entirely in your browser via Pyodide with no server needed. ALM is smaller by design - lean and focused instead of trying to know everything about everything.",

